{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f5939b37d4","title":"中共湖北黄冈地委转发麻城县委关于农村食堂工作的几项规定（草案）","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d99ece0efc","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":10,"articleId":"f5939b37d4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7b15c05f89","type":"title","text":"中共湖北黄冈地委转发麻城县委关于农村食堂工作的几项规定（草案）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"990888dff4","type":"appellation","text":"各县委、并报省委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"7dc8d5e75e","type":"paragraph","text":"这是麻城县委关于农村食堂工作的几项规定（草案），我们认为一般还好，现转发各县委参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"b26361f029","type":"paragraph","text":"地委主张所有农村食堂，要推行饭票、菜票制度，按人定量凭票就餐，月终结余，归本人所得的制度。希各县做食堂工作规定时，能把这一条写进去。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"443e2ddd3a","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共黄冈地委59年4月10日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"581c4843b6","type":"subtitle","text":"中共麻城县委关于农村食堂工作的几项规定（草案）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"9eb4eb2815","type":"paragraph","text":"1，建立食堂要从群众自愿、吃饭方便、有利生产出发。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"1cbcc2a80e","type":"paragraph","text":"2，以生产小队为单位建立食堂管理委员会，统一核算，统一管理。每个小队根据居住条件和人口多少，建立一个或几个食堂。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"e634ea4ade","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）居住集中，人口不多，可以建立一个食堂；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"d8ea38855f","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）居住集中，人口较多，可以建立几个食堂；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"4229d5e971","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）居住分散，可以就垸建立，三家五户也可以建立一个食堂；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"82b0dc7f66","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）远离的单家独户，可以不参加食堂，食堂按供给标准发给伙食费，自己起火。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"7a4662c184","type":"paragraph","text":"3，办好食堂的标准是吃饱吃好吃省。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"37fb0974a1","type":"paragraph","text":"4，实行几定包干，如定人口，定口粮，定伙食费，定种菜和养猪任务，定交肥料任务等。在包干范围内，积极经营，改善生活，结余归食堂所有。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"2a0954d4ca","type":"paragraph","text":"5，实行定工吃饭，旷工付钱。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"2cc2163a38","type":"paragraph","text":"6，社员自己有粮食，自愿在家煮饭，食堂按标准发给伙食费。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"7d91166d99","type":"paragraph","text":"7，食堂的管理人员要经过民主选举。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"262ec7dfd0","type":"paragraph","text":"8，实行民主管理。食堂管理委员会，要经过开社员座谈会，设意见箱，发动社员贴大字报等办法，广泛征求社员对食堂工作的意见。改进工作，满足要求。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"f3eaba9ef7","type":"paragraph","text":"9，每月公布账目一次。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"ff99212d51","type":"paragraph","text":"10，开展食堂之间、服务人员之间的几好几满意的劳动竞赛。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"},{"id":"973d8af3e1","type":"paragraph","text":" 这中共麻城县委员会59年4月7日","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4"}],"page":{"id":"6dfcc12967","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f5939b37d4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}